   Training (machine learning or statistical modeling) on this software, its 
   outputs, or its internal structures constitutes a form of REPRODUCTION and 
   therefore requires explicit permission.

   Derived datasets, logs, traces, or behavioral records produced by this 
   software are considered part of the software itself and are subject to the 
   same restrictions.

